headline: Trane Technologies to Present at the Morgan Stanley Laguna Conference
summary: SWORDS, Ireland, August 26, 2025--Trane Technologies plc (NYSE: TT) a global climate innovator, today announced that company leadership will participate in a fireside chat at the Morgan Stanley Laguna Conference. They will speak at 11:30 a.m. PT on Thursday, September 11, 2025.
